trans-unit.source: Specifies the level of authentication for DCOM security.
The ProcessModelComAuthenticationLevel enumerates the values to use when you set the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProcessModelSection.ComAuthenticationLevel%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: ProcessModelComAuthenticationLevel nummererer verdiene som skal brukes når du angir den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProcessModelSection.ComAuthenticationLevel%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProcessModelSection.ComAuthenticationLevel%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The ProcessModelComAuthenticationLevel settings are relevant only when you use the ASP.NET process model (Internet Information Services [IIS] 5.n or compatible mode on IIS 6 only).
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For ProcessModelComAuthenticationLevel innstillinger er relevante bare når du bruker ASP.NET process model (Internet Information Services [IIS] 5.n eller kompatibel modus i IIS 6).

trans-unit.source: Specifies that DCOM authenticates the credentials of the client.
trans-unit.target: Angir at DCOM godkjenner legitimasjonen for klienten.

trans-unit.source: DCOM authenticates the credentials of the client when the server receives the request at the beginning of each remote procedure call.
trans-unit.target: DCOM godkjenner klientens legitimasjon når serveren mottar forespørsel ved starten av hver eksternt prosedyrekall.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that DCOM authenticates the credentials of the client.
trans-unit.target: Angir at DCOM godkjenner legitimasjonen for klienten.

trans-unit.source: DCOM authenticates the credentials of the client only when the client establishes a relationship with the server.
trans-unit.target: DCOM godkjenner legitimasjonen for klienten bare når klienten oppretter en relasjon med serveren.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that DCOM determines the authentication level.
DCOM determines the authentication level using its normal security-negotiation algorithm.
trans-unit.target: DCOM bestemmer det godkjenning ved hjelp av den vanlige sikkerhet forhandling-algoritmen.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that DCOM verifies that all data received is from the expected client.
trans-unit.target: Angir at DCOM bekrefter at alle data som er mottatt fra klienten forventet.

trans-unit.source: The datagram transports always use Pkt authentication.
trans-unit.target: Datagram transport bruke alltid Pkt godkjenning.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that DCOM authenticates and verifies the data transferred.
trans-unit.target: Angir at DCOM godkjenner og kontrollerer dataene er overført.

trans-unit.source: DCOM verifies that none of the data transferred between the client and the server has been modified.
trans-unit.target: DCOM bekrefter at ingen av dataene som overføres mellom klienten og serveren er endret.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that DCOM authenticates all previous levels and does encryption.
trans-unit.target: Angir at DCOM godkjenner alle tidligere nivåer, og tillater kryptering.

trans-unit.source: DCOM authenticates all previous levels and encrypts the argument value of each remote procedure call.
trans-unit.target: DCOM godkjenner alle tidligere nivåer og krypterer argumentverdien for hver eksternt prosedyrekall.
